You are in project Barekey. A highly modernized, easy to use, vault manager.

This project uses Convex for the backend, Autumn for payments, Shadcn/Tailwind for styling, React SPA (vite) for the web dashboard.

They can login with Google, GitHub and usernameless Passkeys (preferred).

Note that this project has two auth methods:
- Regular sign in for the web UI (session)
- token based sign in for the APIs.

This means that the auth pkg should have a segment in its path for logging in as its two ways.

We simplify projects architecture to preserve code boilerplate. That means that only teams can own projects. Each user automatically gets a org created named "<name>'s Organization". 